metadata.description:
Look closely.

What do you see in this picture? Apartments? Chipped walls? Hanged clothes? Air conditioners? Windows? What I see are 66 unique and untold stories being packed in a 2563x2563 frame.

Where to find them?
Choi Hung Estate, Ngau Chi Wan, Kowloon, Hong Kong
22.335°N 114.206667°E
